# Banned Files
Never commit: `venv/`, `node_modules/`, `__pycache__/`, `playwright-report/`, `test-results/`, `*.zip`, `*.whl`, `*.db`, `.env`, `*.key`, `*.pem`

Never hardcode secrets — use environment variables.
